page.title: 10Health care in Stock
page.content: There are two doctors in Stock their names are Doctor Warden and Doctor Coffin,the doctor's surgery is in the High Street.They haven't any chemists in Stock so the doctors make their own medicine up,they have their own pharmacy.I don't think many people have to go to the doctors because there isn't pollution(well not too much) .Doctor Coffin used to work with Doctor Death,now Doctor Coffin works with Doctor Warden,who is a lady doctor who specialises in women's medicine or gynaecology.The nearest general hospital is in Chelmsford. there distric nurse,and distric Midwife and health visitor in Stock.
